  name_en = '徐汇公学旧址（崇思楼）',
  body = '<p>Detailed Address: No. 68 Hongqiao Road, Xuhui District, Shanghai Ticket Information: Free admission. Group visits should reserve at least 3 working days in advance through Xuhui High School. Opening Hours: Regular weekends: Saturday and Sunday 9:00–16:00. Summer/winter breaks: Tuesday, Thursday, Saturday, and Sunday 9:00–16:00. Open areas include the Chongsi Building first floor, the Huixue Museum, and the Huixue Corridor. Transportation: Subway Lines 1/9/11 to Xujiahui Station, Exit 10, about a 5-minute walk. Buses 855/572 stop at Hongqiao Road. Adjacent to Grand Gateway 66 and Pacific Department Store.</p>',
