  name_zh = '百代小楼（《义勇军进行曲》灌制地纪念馆）',
  name_en = '百代小楼（《义勇军进行曲》灌制地纪念馆）',
  body = '<p>Detailed Address: No. 811 Hengshan Road, Xuhui District, Shanghai (inside Xujiahui Park) Ticket Information: Free admission. Advance reservation via the "Baidai Villa" WeChat account is required; slots fill up quickly on holidays. Opening Hours: Tuesday to Sunday 9:00–17:00 (last entry 16:30), closed Mondays, except on national holidays. Transportation: Subway Lines 1/9 to Xujiahui Station, Exit 14, about an 8-minute walk. Buses 15/42/43/50/167 stop at Xujiahui. The villa is at the corner of Hengshan Road and Wanping Road, near the Xujiahui Park fountain plaza.</p>',
